<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Abstract Thought • atiyah saleemah</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --orange: #ff4d00;
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--orange);
            color: white;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            padding: 3rem 5% 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        header p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .articles-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem 5%;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .card {
            background: #0DE616;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.4s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 1.8rem;
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card p {
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.45;
        }

        .back-home {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 2rem 5%;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>[the abstract thought]</h1>
        <p>Deep thoughts, observations, and reflections.</p>
    </header>

    <a href="index.html" class="back-home">← Back to Home</a>

